{
  "stem": "20089.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that house a-- Bavarian villa in Munich, which had about 15 rooms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in each room was a survivor family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he took me and introduced me to every member of the family that had survived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Each one was in one room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were friends as well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And each one grabbed me and started telling me their horror stories, and for the first time that I had actually heard about the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't think the word Holocaust was then a word.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was the first time that I heard any of these horror stories.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I reported to the AJDC director, Seal, I said to her, look, I don't want to stay.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I want to go home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't want to hear any more of these stories.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she became very angry with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said, do you think that we spent our money to bring you to have a good time?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just pull yourself together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't listen to the stories here, but don't listen, because if you think you're going home, you're not.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I suddenly, through some kind of shock treatment, realized that I was here to work in Munich.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was there to work and not to enjoy myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had to report to Seal first.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after a few days-- I stayed with my uncle at this villa, listening to these stories.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to report to Seal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she decided that the best for me would be to go to the children's center, because I was very young.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so she sent me off to Rosenheim, which was a very large center.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was an old army-- old German barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it had at the time 3,000 children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were arranged in-- like kibbutz groups.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
